its. In that same year, a trio of hags declared the sovereignty of the new nation of Droaam.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.4;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;color:#222222;font-family:ff-good-web-pro;font-size:13.8667px;margin-top:0px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-left:0px !important;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:ff-good-web-pro\"> </span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.4;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;color:#222222;font-family:ff-good-web-pro;font-size:13.8667px;margin-top:0px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-left:0px !important;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:ff-good-web-pro\"><a href=\"https://eberron.fandom.com/wiki/Droaam\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click here for more info on Droaam</a></span></p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":850000,"name":"The Mror Holds","type":"text","_id":"2SeJ30L0pFwzxDc9","title":{"show":true,"level":2},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;font-weight:bolder\"><span style=\"font-family:ff-good-web-pro\"><strong>Government</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-family:ff-good-web-pro\"> Oligarchy</span></p><p class=\"hang\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.4;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding-left:1em;text-indent:-1em;color:#222222;font-family:ff-good-web-pro;font-size:13.8667px;margin-top:0px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-left:0px !important;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1;text-rendering:optimize